All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
public class ExpansionItem
extends IdentityItem

An ExpansionItem contains information about why a value was expanded in a provisioning plan as a result of plan compilation. This contains information that identifies the expanded value (application, native identity, name, value, etc...) and information about the expansion (why did it happen).
